    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Plan a Trip to Disney World\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to help you plan a trip to Disney World. \r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Start by entering a **generic prompt** and read AI Chat's response. For example: \r\n\r\n>Help me plan a trip to Disney World\r\n2. *Revise your prompt* and add specific examples, like **what rides you want to go on** or **which characters you want to meet**. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's updated response.\r\n2. Finally, re-submit your previous prompt and **add some images**.\r\n3. Press **Send** and read AI Chat's response.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n\r\n::: details [<i class=\"fa fa-file-image-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **How do I add an image?**]\r\n- Click the button labeled **Add** below your chat input.\r\n- Choose **From Library**\r\n- Then browse the existing images.\r\n- When you have an image to upload, click the checkbox next to it to select it and then click **Attach**.\r\n- You should see the image get added to the message being sent to AI Chat.\r\n:::\r\n",
